{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"9f204fac31","title":"右派言论——反对肃反运动","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"8f5f72ad6a","index":0,"year":1957,"month":5,"day":null,"articleId":"9f204fac31"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"5378a8871a","name":"学生"},{"id":"5841b1c66b","name":"上海财经学院"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"7bb7218307","type":"title","text":"右派言论——反对肃反运动","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9f204fac31"},{"id":"44055e899a","type":"authors","text":"上海财经学院学生","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9f204fac31"},{"id":"6dea26b68f","type":"paragraph","text":"(1)“肃反搞不好，真正的没有肃，好人肃了。”","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9f204fac31"},{"id":"114e59c3d5","type":"paragraph","text":"(2)“我院肃反是错误的，把好人当反革命斗。”","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9f204fac31"},{"id":"e8644d1c51","type":"paragraph","text":"(3)“班上肃反搞错了，我当时就有意见，只是怕扣帽子不敢说。”","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9f204fac31"},{"id":"66554c1a0a","type":"paragraph","text":"(4)“周璇是因‘肃反’，‘思改’把她搞得神经错乱的。”","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9f204fac31"},{"id":"50d0de3ad8","type":"paragraph","text":"(5)“在苏州发现有一地方失火，公安机关一定要查出几个反革命分子来凑数，这些人头脑中以公式化的办法来处理肃反问题。”","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9f204fac31"},{"id":"6ab4f5ca1f","type":"paragraph","text":"(6)×××认为自己父亲是由于镇反，劳动改造才引起死亡的，所以说：“政府乱加罪名，无中生有。”","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9f204fac31"},{"id":"eb695c12e0","type":"paragraph","text":"(7)“胡风问题中央处理不当，中央已在重新处理。”","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9f204fac31"},{"id":"775bf4d983","type":"paragraph","text":"(8)“我处在流沙河的地位，同样会写出这样的文章来。”","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9f204fac31"},{"id":"83f8086b75","type":"paragraph","text":"(9)“肃反中我们采取的方法是粗暴的，有的动拳头，有的打耳光，以致每晚都有人自杀，这样积下的仇恨，使阶级斗争尖锐化隐蔽起来，他们不杀我们杀谁?”","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9f204fac31"},{"id":"261be19fbb","type":"appellation","text":"(10)“肃反中有好些地方都是未经检查研究，……有些人心血来潮，不根据事实讲话，应冷静些看问题。”","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9f204fac31"},{"id":"71197c483d","type":"paragraph","text":"(11)“肃反、三反是凭硬打逼出问题来的，在运动中不准支持正义。”","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9f204fac31"},{"id":"460ee93152","type":"paragraph","text":"(12)“肃反在全国是有成绩的，对我个人是没有成绩的，我永远记在心里。”","index":13,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9f204fac31"},{"id":"db394b5480","type":"paragraph","text":" 来源：《反右派斗争言论选辑　第一辑　学生部份》（中共上海财经学院委员会编，1957年9","index":14,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9f204fac31"}],"page":{"id":"a09bbcc297","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9f204fac31","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}